{"id":190969,"link":"https://chinadigitaltimes.net/chinese/2011/10/来看看哪还不用facebook/","date":"2011-10-23T18:00:09Z","modified":"2011-10-23T18:06:43Z","title":"来看看哪还不用Facebook","content":"<p><p>译者  <a href=\"http://space.yeeyan.org/u/154194\">yuoio</a></p>\n<p><img src=\"http://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/unfacebook-625x311.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /></p>\n<p>还记得前一阵的那幅<a href=\"http://flowingdata.com/2010/12/13/facebook-worldwide-friendships-mapped/\">Facebook连通图</a>吗？那幅图片通过一条条弧线展示了全球连入Facebook的地方的数字化社交关系。视觉艺术专业的研究生Ian Wojtowicz将NASA著名的“<a href=\"http://geology.com/articles/satellite-photo-earth-at-night.shtml\">晚间地球</a>”与那幅Facebook连通图结合起来制成了这张图，上面你所看到的就是。(译者注：晚间地球是NASA制作的一幅卫星图，在卫星图上展示了世界各地的电力消费情况）</p>\n<p>黑色区域代表了Facebook覆盖的区域，黄色区域是不使用Facebook的地方。看起来很像Thorsten Gaetz的<a href=\"http://flowingdata.com/2010/12/15/filling-in-the-black-holes-of-the-facebook-friendship-map/\">那幅图</a>，却有着更高的颗粒度。</p>\n<p>来张亚洲的近景:</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/Asia-unfacebook.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /> </p>\n<p>还有南美洲的:</p>\n<p> <img src=\"http://flowingdata.com/wp-content/uploads/2011/10/South-America-unfacebook.png\" alt=\"\" border=\"0\" /><br /> <span>看，很简单。让我困惑的是还有什么图能结合在一起呢？</span><br /> <span><br /> </span></p>\n<p>[<a href=\"http://station.woj.com/2011/07/unfacebook-world.html\">The UnFacebook World</a> | Thanks, Ian]</p>\n<p><img src=\"http://www1.feedsky.com/t1/569250123/yeeyan/feedsky/s.gif?r=http://article.yeeyan.org/view/154194/226499\" border=\"0\" height=\"0\" width=\"0\" /></p>\n<p><small>本文由自动聚合程序取自网络，内容和观点不代表数字时代立场</small></p>\n<form method=\"POST\" action=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/f.fbz?AddNewUserDirect\">\n定期获得翻墙信息？<a href=\"http://www.feedblitz.com/f/?Sub=738338\">请电邮订阅数字时代</a> <br /><input name=\"EMAIL\" maxlength=\"64\" type=\"text\" size=\"25\" value=\"\"><br />\n<input name=\"FEEDID\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"738338\"><br />\n<input name=\"PUBLISHER\" type=\"hidden\" value=\"7485568\"><br />\n<input type=\"submit\" value=\"订阅!\"><br />\n</form>\n","author":993,"categories":[10466,13770,20534],"tags":[]}